  "description": "A fairly advanced and easy-to-use two-chamber refrigerator with separate cooling circuits for the working chambers, presented on the market by the popular brand Siemens in 2023. Stainless steel with a protective EasyClean coating is used for the exterior finish of the model. The MultiAirflow multi-flow cooling system is responsible for distributing the cold inside the working chambers. The circulation circuit is double, due to which the cold flows between the cooling and freezing zones do not mix. The HyperFresh 0C freshness zone is available, which is designed for longer storage of fresh vegetables and fruits. The two-chamber refrigerator Siemens KG49NAIBT has improved side lighting, which makes the cooling chamber more comfortable. An effective stainless steel edging is used for the shelves and drawers - metal pads help stabilize the temperature regime, and also improve the aesthetics of the interior. The cooling chamber door is equipped with an external screen, which is automatically activated when the door is opened. This refrigerator supports zero-gap installation. The model can be installed in a niche, it can be safely placed under walls and next to furniture. The freezing chamber has a -24 °C mode. The freezer is capable of autonomously maintaining cold for 21 hours.",
